                                       `mongosh --eval 'rs.status()'`
  elchi-stack ch-client [args...]     open clickhouse-client locally as the
                                       \`elchi\` user (CH-node only — first 3)
  elchi-stack ssh <node> [cmd...]     open SSH to a cluster node using the
                                       persisted cluster key. <node> = m1/m2/m3,
                                       hostname, or IP. No args → interactive
                                       admin-user shell; with args → run them
