                                       holes + lossy links that plain TCP checks
                                       miss). --mesh: every node probes every
                                       other node → full src×dst matrix (M1 +
                                       root; uses the persisted SSH creds).
                                       [--timeout=3] [--samples=3]
                                       [--icmp-count=10] [--json]
                                       exit: 0 clean · 1 any FAIL / MTU black
